# Adding a New Business Unit

## 1. Request Accounts Created in Modernisation Platform

The accounts should be member accounts and should include both non-live and live environments.

For example:

`container-platform-bu-nonlive`

and

`container-platform-bu-live`

[Modernisation Platform new account guide](https://user-guide.modernisation-platform.service.justice.gov.uk/user-guide/creating-environments.html)

## 2. Add to the CP accounts.json

Add the account to the [terraform/environments/cloud-platform/accounts.json](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/terraform/environments/cloud-platform/accounts.json) file in the Modernisation Platform Environments repo.

## 3. Create the Terraform Workspace

The Terraform workspace will automatically be created in the `container-platform-bu` application folder.
However, we run Terraform from the `cloud-platform` application folder, so we need to create the workspace there.

This should be done using the [generate-account-workspaces.sh](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/terraform/environments/cloud-platform/generate-account-workspaces.sh) script. This ensures workspaces are created for all of the accounts in the `accounts.json` file.

## 4. Add Root Subdomain

In the `cloud-platform` root folder, add the subdomain for the business unit to the [environment configuration](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/terraform/environments/cloud-platform/environment-configuration.tf#L2).

## 5. Add BU to Skip Plan Evaluator

Add the new accounts to the [skip plan evaluator file](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/.github/config/skip-plan-evaluator-workspaces.json) in the MPE config folder.

## 6. Add the VPC CIDR

Add the allocated VPC CIDR to the `vpc_cidr` block in [network locals](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/terraform/environments/cloud-platform/network/locals.tf#L17).

## 7. RAM Share MP TGW to New Accounts

See code example [here](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform/blob/main/terraform/environments/core-network-services/ram.tf#L16).

## 8. Add New Accounts to TGW Routes

See code example [here](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform/blob/main/terraform/environments/core-network-services/container_platform_tgw_connections.tf#L4).

## 9. Apply Workflows to Build Out Clusters

Apply the cloud-platform and container-platform workflows.

## 10. Add Route 53 Records for the New BU Subdomain

See code example [here](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/terraform/environments/cloud-platform/route53.tf#L66).

## 11. Add the New BU to External DNS

See code example [here](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/modernisation-platform-environments/blob/main/terraform/environments/cloud-platform/cluster-core/external-dns.tf#L18).
